title: Joe Rogan Destroys Adam Ruins Everything
description:
Music: www.purple-planet.com
In this video I continue my discussion on Adam Conover, the host of TruTV's show Adam Ruins Everything. I continue where I left off on the discussion on sports, then move on to the subject Adam decided to bring up. I explain why I don't think this was a good move for Adam, & why I believe this part of the interview reveals more about Adam's thought process than any other part.
